Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在最后几个大的任务当中，我想要解决的是\NAnd one of the last big tasks that I wanna tackle is adaptive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个应用的自适应布局\Nlayout for an application.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,回想一下我们要完成的目标：\NRecall what we wanted to accomplish was to take
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们处于条形状态\Nthe details from the right and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要把右边的细节内容转移到列表的下方去\Nmove it under the list whenever we're in a narrow layout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.48,0:00:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们足够宽的时候\NBut when we're in a wide layout,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就想要它回到右边原来的位置\Nthen we want it to be where it's at right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我们添加一个视觉状态管理器\NSo we'll add a VisualState Manager and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一些状态，然后让它工作\Nsome VisualStates, and we'll get it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在下一节视频中我们会为应用添上最后的功能\NAnd then we'll do any cleanup on the UI that we need to
