Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所有我们现在就从这里开始吧\NSo let's go ahead and get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这个上一节中添加的这个格子下面\NI'm going to, underneath this first grid that I added in
